    <item>
      <title>卢拉的竞争对手在关键市长选举前煽动对犯罪的恐惧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/lula-s-rivals-stoke-fear-over-crime-before-key-mayoral-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在巴西即将举行的市长选举中，人们对犯罪问题的担忧占据了主导地位。周日的选举是对巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦及其所支持的候选人的一次考验，也是对其政府的一次早期全民公投。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/lula-s-rivals-stoke-fear-over-crime-before-key-mayoral-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经过数月战斗，乌克兰前哨基地落入俄军手中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/ukraine-outpost-falls-to-russian-forces-after-months-of-fighting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着俄罗斯军队缓慢推进自 2022 年初入侵以来克里姆林宫一直瞄准的领土，乌克兰军队从顿涅茨克地区东部前线的一个战略前哨撤出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/ukraine-outpost-falls-to-russian-forces-after-months-of-fighting</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 07:43:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列誓言对伊朗大规模导弹袭击进行报复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/israel-vows-retaliation-for-massive-iranian-missile-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗向以色列发射了约 200 枚弹道导弹，导致两国之间的敌对状态严重升级，世界大国担心这可能演变成一场中东战争。本杰明内塔尼亚胡誓言要对伊朗进行报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/israel-vows-retaliation-for-massive-iranian-missile-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 07:06:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>丹麦加强以色列大使馆附近安保以调查爆炸事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/denmark-boosts-security-near-israeli-embassy-as-blasts-probed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[夜间附近发生两起爆炸事件后，丹麦警方加强了以色列驻哥本哈根大使馆周围的安全保卫。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/denmark-boosts-security-near-israeli-embassy-as-blasts-probed</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 06:24:44 GMT</pubDate>
